\pard\sa160\f0\fs32 \b 24th FAI European Gliding Championships \u8212? Overview\par
\pard\sa40\f0\fs22 \b Entry list and field composition\par
\pard\sa40\f0\fs18 Ostr\u243?w Wielkopolski Micha\u322?k\u243?w, Poland \u183? 11\u8211?25 July 2026 \u183? Contest 5337\par
\pard\sa200\f0\fs16 Source: soaringspot MCP server (contest 5337), endpoints get_contest / get_contest_classes / get_class_contestants. Generated 2026-06-05.\par
\pard\sa80\f0\fs24 \b Status\par
\pard\sa120\f0\fs18 The championship has not yet started (it opens 11 July 2026). Entry lists are published, but \b no tasks have been set and no results exist\b0  \u8212? get_class_tasks returns 404 and get_contest_winners is empty. This report covers the registered field only.\par
\pard\sa80\f0\fs24 \b Summary\par
\pard\sa120\f0\fs18 88 pilots registered across 3 single-seater classes, representing 22 nations \u8212? 20 European plus two guest nations (Argentina and Israel, in Standard class).\par
