\pard\sa120\f0\fs16 Notes: All three classes are single-seaters, so entries equal pilots. Nationality is taken from each contestant's pilot record. Argentina and Israel are non-European guest entries in Standard class \u8212? they normally fly but do not count toward the European title. Aircraft are predominantly JS3 / AS33 / Ventus 2 / Diana 2 (15 Metre), LS3 / LS4 / ASW-20 / Discus / SZD (Club), and LS8 / Discus 2a (Standard).\par
\pard\sa120\f0\fs16 Once the contest is flying, per-task points, daily and cumulative standings, and final podiums can be added from get_task_points, get_class_results and get_contest_winners.\par
